en.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer

Starring: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Production House: Rusk Studios
Produced By: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Directed By: Tanmai Rastogi
Developed, Story, Screenplay and Written by: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romance
 
About Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, a small-town boxer from Safidon, enters Delhiâ€™s elite St. Collins college to fulfill his brotherâ€™s dream of becoming a polished, English-speaking graduate. Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla â€” a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever â€” this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is Indiaâ€™s leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Whoâ€™s your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter â€“ Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more!

Amazon MX Player presenteert
Aukaat Ke Bahar - OfficiÃ«le trailer

Met in de hoofdrollen: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Productiehuis: Rusk Studios
Geproduceerd door: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Regie: Tanmai Rastogi
Ontwikkeld, verhaal, scenario en scenario door: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romantiek

Over Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, een bokser uit een klein stadje in Safidon, gaat naar de elite St. Collins College in Delhi om de droom van zijn broer te verwezenlijken: een verfijnde, Engelstalige student. Te midden van pesterijen, cultuurschokken en klassenverschillen wordt hij verliefd op Antara Shukla â€“ een laatstejaarsstudent met politieke aspiraties die ver buiten zijn bereik ligt. Wanneer een vernederende uitdaging botst met zijn groeiende gevoelens en een familiecrisis thuis, moet Rajveer harder vechten dan ooit â€“ dit keer niet voor glorie, maar voor liefde, waardigheid en overleving.

Over Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is India's toonaangevende gratis, premium, advertentie-ondersteunde entertainmentdienst. The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

Thank You So Much For Watching!
Stay Tuned! Stay Buzzed!

The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

Thank You So Much For Watching!
Stay Tuned! Stay Buzzed!

Lyrics: 
Pallavi 
Ratnamalaa !! Ratnamala !!  
Nannu veedi nuvvala poraadhey.  
Ratnamalaa !! Ratnamala !!  
Minnu veedi vennela poraadhey  
Ulagame suzhalvadhean? 
Udhiriyaai udaivadhean? 
yetho noolondril varaindha 
Kurippu poley tholaindheneyâ€¦ 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Ennai vittu needhaan neengaadhey 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadheyâ€¦ 

Chorus 
Vaalai Kumari penne 
Vandhaan Kumaran ponne 
Solai pookkalin munne 
Olai vidu thoodhu kanne 

Chorus 
Nenjam adhu enna kallo 
Manjam ini aagum mullo 
Vanjam seyvaalo paavai 
Thanjam adhu undhan paadhai (paavai) 

Charanam 1 
Oh.. Oh.. Adiye neeyum nalamaa? 
Kadidham solli vidumaa? 
Meiyodu mutham kalandhuvaithathai 
En aasai solla vaarthai theerndhadhaiâ€¦ 
Un pirivil nagal nogudhey 
En paruvam madal yerudhey 
Pen uruvam nizhalaanadhe 
Mei sera, maaneâ€¦! 

Chorus 
Vaalai Kumari penne 
Vandhaan Kumaran ponne 
Solai pookkalin munne 
Olai vidu thoodhu kanne 

Chorus 
Nenjam adhu enna kallo 
Manjam ini aagum mullo 
Vanjam seyvaalo paavai 
Thanjam adhu undhan paadhai (paavai) 

Pallavi Repeat 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadheyâ€¦ 

Charanam 2 
Oh.. Oh.. Azhageâ€¦ idhazh oram, melidhaai 
Muruval koodum 
Karum mega kootil minnal keetru polâ€¦ 
Araipulli yodu neelum paattai polâ€¦ 
Viral idukkin peana munai 
Idam maatru neeyum adhaiâ€¦ 
Un meani theendidum vaira 
Madalthaalum naaneâ€¦ 

Pallavi Final 
Ulagame suzhalvadhean? 
Udhiriyaai udaivadhean? 
yetho noolondril varaindha 
Kurippu poley tholaindheneyâ€¦ 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Ennai vittu needhaan neengaadhey 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadheyâ€¦

Franklin Opens Every HAUNTED Mystery Container In Indian Bike Driving 3D! ğŸ˜±
